  "title": "MARKETING EXECUTIVE",
  "description": "<p><strong>🎯 About the Role</strong></p><p>The Marketing Executive will be part of a dynamic, hands-on marketing team driving brand story across digital, retail, and event platforms.</p><p>This role is ideal for someone with creative flair, curiosity about technology, and ambition to grow into a senior or managerial marketing position in the near future.<br /></p><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong><br /></p><p><strong>🚀 What You’ll Do</strong><br /></p><p><strong>1️⃣ Digital & Social Media Marketing</strong></p><p>Plan, execute, and optimise campaigns on Meta, TikTok, Google, Shopee, and Lazada.</p><p>Manage posting schedules, analytics, and content calendar.</p><p>Work with creative and video teams to craft engaging visuals and copy.<br /></p><p><strong>2️⃣ Content Creation & Storytelling</strong></p><p>Develop brand stories that connect emotionally with audiences.</p><p>Support lifestyle photoshoots, product videos, and campaign ideation.</p><p>Keep content fresh, trendy, and aligned with brand’s tone.<br /></p><p><strong>3️⃣ Event & Retail Marketing</strong></p><p>Assist in event promotions, product launches, and exhibition shows.</p><p>Coordinate printed collaterals and booth visuals with design partners.<br /></p><p><strong>4️⃣ Collaboration & Reporting</strong></p><p>Work closely with the sales and CS teams to align marketing support with business goals.</p><p>Track campaign performance, analyse insights, and propose improvements.<br /></p><p><strong>💡 What We’re Looking For</strong></p><p>· Diploma or Degree in Marketing, Communications, or related field.</p><p>· 1–3 years of relevant experience in digital marketing, creative content, or brand management (fresh grads with strong portfolios welcome!).</p><p>· Proficient in social media tools and marketing platforms.</p><p>· Creative thinker with excellent written and visual sense.</p><p>· Organised, adaptable, and eager to learn new tools and trends.</p><p>· Comfortable working in a fast-moving environment with clear KPIs.</p><p>· Bilingual in English and Mandarin is an advantage.<br /></p><p><strong>💼 What We Offer</strong></p><p>✅ Competitive Salary</p><p>✅ 5-Day Work Week (Mon–Fri, 9am–6pm)</p><p>✅ Annual Leave, Birthday Leave, Medical Benefits</p><p>✅ Friendly, fast-growing work environment with career progression</p><p>✅ Opportunities for regional exposure and cross-border projects<br /></p><p><strong>💬 Join Our Mission</strong></p><p>If you love creativity, smart design, and meaningful marketing — is where your career grows alongside innovation.</p><p>📧 Apply now with your resume & portfolio:</p><p>👉 yuplussolutions@gmail.com</p>",
